  "text": "All ultrasound data were collected and managed using Research Electronic Data Capture (REDCap ® , Vanderbilt University, Nashville, TN, USA) [CITATION_1] before surgery and not changed thereafter. The ultrasound examiner was unaware of the results of any additional imaging, if performed.",
